{"tid":579871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【航空母艦新解】「形容女人身軀龐大」台灣教育部成語典被轟歧視","createTime":"2018-03-04T04:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T05:05:29.000Z","uid":122,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd897ad072a074f6e0b168216a9b7b6fa4ddcba3","tid":579871,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:17:56.000Z","msg":"【航空母艦新解】「形容女人身軀龐大」台教育部成語典被轟歧視<br />\n<br />\n即時兩岸 <br />\n<br />\n2018-03-03 17:45:46 HKT<br />\n<br />\n台灣教育部辭典解釋令人咋舌，刊出「航空母艦」的第2個解釋竟為「形容女人身軀龐大」。<br />\n<br />\n2007年初，教育部辭典將「三隻小豬」等字詞列入成語，引發各界熱議。近來有網友發現，在教育部成語典，輸入「航空母艦」，得到2種意涵，平日揶揄身材的玩笑話，竟列入官方辭典的解釋。<br />\n<br />\n教育部成語典查詢「航空母艦」，第1種解釋是「能載運轟炸機、魚雷機及戰鬥機等攻擊武器的大型軍艦。有廣大的飛行甲板，以供各型飛機起落。指揮臺及其他操縱設備則位於甲板旁側，並配有對空武器以自我防衛。」<br />\n<br />\n但成語典第2個解釋是「形容女人身軀龐大」，還造句舉例：「她的身材，真像航空母艦」。網友感到不滿，如此解釋及例句有性別、身材歧視的味道，竟還收錄在教育部官方的成語典，覺得不妥當。"},{"pid":"0f91dde05b54290a281f10ca5c4384a1e6fc0037","tid":579871,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6beb8c1e0ef2740e4361992274be91b53e03e52e","tid":579871,"uid":63452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"電單車 嘅同義詞？"},{"pid":"a25559ea75d4d4651af4b8dd4681261e3729ea3d","tid":579871,"uid":43009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"咁毒撚係咪隱形戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed80dd7c0907d75d14a348c20ca4cd8fe6b322eb","tid":579871,"uid":44118,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"a25559ea75d4d4651af4b8dd4681261e3729ea3d","tid":579871,"uid":43009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"咁毒撚係咪隱形戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"唔怪得知係街成日見到毒撚同肥婆拖手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c39914a1a37af5bd0552539a046b30f48bd139","tid":579871,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"「濶過航空母艦」都唔係講身形 SIZE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6102b47add03c34e6fc537b9d39c8a3f6d3cbf3","tid":579871,"uid":38416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"加埋肥過電單車 ok?"},{"pid":"974f7e06cedb00518c2b79754c61cd6850a26979","tid":579871,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"呢D似容詞點會入字典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad88a1b4aa9a2bb7a9263cff67fb21d388f7a7b2","tid":579871,"uid":110832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"台灣呢撚都亂鳩咁黎"},{"pid":"d743fb8684762cd27db81639b329ad39515fc84e","tid":579871,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"掂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073c86a81681fda37dcba2c292870f3275fde97a","tid":579871,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"航空母艦形容肥閪港女最適合"},{"pid":"1f7cdbb3e9aa78512a3110b6eb106eda21a1da50","tid":579871,"uid":5159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"建議牛津都將 iPad 加入字典: 形容港女波平如鏡, 而且有錢就可以摸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b628c6f369efdf9546c1af89a6c3332cbdad6ebb","tid":579871,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"乜唔係太空坦克咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2a496290a1ce1d93526a7f891b21b1d4447c98","tid":579871,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"直到她十三歲那一年，因為在錄影廠吃着一條大香腸，給記者拍照後，以「航空母艦」形容她，欣宜傷心得哭了。肥姐好心疼，看着女兒的眼淚，她心痛之極。"}]}